<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-2126] Remove Log4J API dependency on Management APIs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2126</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please consider removing dependency on Java Management APIs from Log4J API module in order to improve compatibility with Android Platform that does not support JMX extensions. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is a regression introduced in 2.9.1. Please see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1926&quot; title=&quot;Remove dependency on RMI and Management APIs from log4j-api&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-1926&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-1926&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for details.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
